Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The reunification of Germany and Mayor Edward Koch
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00ydt79
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 22 Sep 1989
An analysis of the potential perils of a unified Germany, a profile of Edward Koch, the Mayor of New York, and a recollection of the reign of Mayor Fiorello La Guardia.